                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/3369" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0817</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10861 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海信“揽入”东芝电视：“嫁女”背后的亲家博弈</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hisense Acquired Toshiba TV Business: The Negotiation between Two Business Groups</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘素，陈志军</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海信，东芝</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家电行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">跨国并购；品牌授权；竞标；尽职调查；谈判；2018百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">cross border mergers and acquisitions; brand authorization; bidding; due diligence; negotiation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018年7月28日，海信集团旗下上市公司海信电器以3.5亿元的最终交割价格完成对东芝映像解决方案公司（简称TVS）95%股权的收购。转让完成后，海信电器不仅享有了东芝电视产品、运营服务等一揽子业务，还拥有东芝电视未来40年的品牌使用权。虽然这起引发轰动的跨国并购吸引了媒体的竞相报道和业界的广泛热议，但是这个并购，从海信最初的竞标、到尽职调查、再到谈判的故事，却鲜为人知。这个过程中很多收购方没有对外批露的考量和做法，实际上对它收购后能否成功运营至关重要。面对“好女不愁嫁”的东芝，海信该怎样设计竞标价格以便能在一众“求娶者”中脱颖而出？面对披着“神秘面纱”的TVS，“局外人”的海信如何做好至关重要的尽职调查？在刀光剑影的谈判中，海信又是怎样与东芝斗志斗勇，有理有据地维护自身的利益？本案例期望通过真实再现海信并购东芝电视过程中的所思所为，为未来更多中国企业的跨国并购提供参考和启示。
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">On July 28, 2018, Hisense electronics, a listed company under Hisense group, completed the acquisition of a 95% stake in the Toshiba Visual Solutions Corporation (TVS) with a final delivery price of 350 million RMB. After the completion of the transfer, Hisense electrical appliances not only owned a package of Toshiba TV products, operation service and so on, but also had the right to use the brand of Toshiba TV for the next 40 years.Although this sensational cross-border M &amp;A had attracted the media&#39;s competing reports and a wide range of hot discussions in the industry, many stories in the merger, from Hisense&#39;s original bidding, to due diligence, and to the negotiations, were rarely known. In the process, many acquirers did not disclose the consideration and negotiation details. In fact, it is very important for the successful operation of the acquirer.
In the face of Toshiba, how could Hisense design a competitive price to stand out among a number of bidders? In the face of the TVS with mysterious veil, how could Hisense, a &quot;outsider&quot;, make a crucial due diligence? How did Hisense fight against Toshiba in the fierce competing negotiation? This case is expected to provide reference and enlightenment for the future transnational mergers and acquisitions of Chinese enterprises through the deal process of Hisense’s acquisition of Toshiba TV.
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《国际企业管理》、《国际市场营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">跨国并购</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018-09</td>
                            </tr>
